﻿in the car together,
when we were 10 years old?

1512
01:46:49,633 --> 01:46:51,228
﻿You helped me so much.

1513
01:46:51,369 --> 01:46:52,756
﻿It wasn't me.

1514
01:46:52,896 --> 01:46:53,451
﻿What?

1515
01:46:54,320 --> 01:46:56,436
﻿I didn't take the blame.
