1516
01:46:56,577 --> 01:46:58,867
﻿who put the rifle in my hand
and told my father

1517
01:46:58,973 --> 01:46:59,978
﻿that it was me.

1518
01:47:00,952 --> 01:47:04,561
﻿-That's not how I remember it.
