01:48:27,613 --> 01:48:28,792
﻿and you leave.

1543
01:48:29,488 --> 01:48:32,750
﻿I never want to see you again.

1544
01:48:34,938 --> 01:48:37,299
﻿I remember what my father
used to say:

1545
01:48:38,029 --> 01:48:39,138
﻿Sometimes you have

1546
